    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[关闭蓝牙的绝对音量]]></title>
        <id>https://ArcMantis.github.io/blog/turn-off-absolute-volume</id>
        <link href="https://ArcMantis.github.io/blog/turn-off-absolute-volume"/>
        <updated>2026-04-20T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[买了个蓝牙音箱,多少有点毛病.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>买了个蓝牙音箱,多少有点毛病.</p>
<ol>
<li class="">博主点击音箱的音量+按钮,会把系统音量改变.并且每次改变的幅度还很大.要么过大,要么太小,做不到细腻的调节.</li>
<li class="">博主滑动电脑音量条,发现如果调整非常小的话,音量会无变化.这个范围是6左右,也就是说一般情况下音量+1和+5是没有区别的.</li>
</ol>
<!-- -->
<h1>如果你的电脑是Linux</h1>
<p>博主系统是debian13,用的是Pipewire和wireplumber结构.如果你的电脑满足以下2个要求就可以用我这个方法.<br>
<!-- -->1.执行下面的指令,如果能正确执行且出现了pipewire字样,就可以.</p>
<div class="language-shell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">wpctl status</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<p>2.执行下面的命令可以查看wireplumber的版本,版本在0.5以上.</p>
<div class="language-shell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">wireplumber --version</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="1创建目录">1.创建目录<a href="https://arcmantis.github.io/blog/turn-off-absolute-volume#1%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95" class="hash-link" aria-label="1.创建目录的直接链接" title="1.创建目录的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<div class="language-shell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">mkdir -p ~/.config/wireplumber/wireplumber.conf.d</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="2编辑文件">2.编辑文件<a href="https://arcmantis.github.io/blog/turn-off-absolute-volume#2%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6" class="hash-link" aria-label="2.编辑文件的直接链接" title="2.编辑文件的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<div class="language-text codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">vim ~/.config/wireplumber/wireplumber.conf.d/80-bluez-properties.conf</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="3-输入下面的内容">3 输入下面的内容<a href="https://arcmantis.github.io/blog/turn-off-absolute-volume#3-%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9" class="hash-link" aria-label="3 输入下面的内容的直接链接" title="3 输入下面的内容的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<div class="language-shell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"> monitor.bluez.properties = {</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">   bluez5.enable-hw-volume = false</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"> }</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<p>最后最好是重启电脑,然后就可以实现音箱物理按钮和系统音量的分离</p>]]></content>
        <author>
            <name>老查</name>
